		<div class="content">
		<br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">﻿</span>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: x-large;"><strong>中央民族乐团新年音乐会</strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: x-large;"><strong>（张家港站）</strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><strong>时间：2012年12月29日                        地点：张家港体育馆  </strong><strong>              </strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><strong>指挥：阎伯政（国家一级指挥）        主持：王军（国家一级演员）</strong></span></p>
 
<p> </p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">一、</span>合奏《茉莉花》                                                                             江苏民歌  刘文金改编</span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">二、二胡、大提琴与乐队《菊花台》                                                 周杰伦曲  陈燮阳编曲</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                           二胡演奏：段超（金钟奖获奖者）</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                   大提琴演奏<span style="font-family: 宋体;">：</span>王崇武（多项国际比赛获奖者）</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">三、女声三重唱《女人花》                                                                     李安修词  陈耀川曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                演唱：郑丽红、赵娜、汤佳</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                  伴奏：马 芸、尹秋薇等</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">四、男声合唱《澧水船夫号子》                                                     根据湖南民歌  营震编曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                        领唱：张平（国家一级演员）、张向华</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">五、女声独唱《我是中国人》                                                                     石飞词  谷建芬曲</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                  演唱：王紫菲（中华社会救助基金会形象大使）</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">六、民歌联唱                                                             王洛宾根据新疆民歌改编  王丹红编配</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                《阿拉木汗》                                                                                      维吾尔族民歌 </span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                          演唱：刘 扬</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                          （文化部文华奖获奖者、文化部首届中国歌剧节获奖者）</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                《可爱的一朵玫瑰花》                                                 哈萨克族民歌  丁善德改编</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                              演唱： 贾静思（第六届东方旋律国际音乐节获奖者）</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">七、琵琶独奏《琵琶语》                                                                         林海曲  吴玉霞编曲</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                          琵琶演奏：吴玉霞</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                              （国家一级演员、文化部优秀剧目展演优秀奖获奖者）</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">八、女声表演唱《这山唱那山》                                                       根据苗族侗族音乐整编</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                <br />                                   ————————    中场休息    ————————<br /></span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><br />九、男声四重唱《香巴拉并不遥远》                                                                 黄志龙词  边洛曲</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                   《娜鲁湾情歌》                                                                     台湾民歌  晓源编曲</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                           演唱：张向华、肖笑、刘松焘、赵健</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">十、京胡与乐队《夜深沉》                                                                     京剧曲牌  吴华改编</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                          京胡演奏：李福华（国家一级演员）</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                          京二胡演奏：刘湘（国家一级演员）</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                           司鼓：李文博</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">十一、男声独唱《山丹丹开花红艳艳》                                                                    陕北民歌</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                             演唱：陈建强（星光大道无冕之王）</span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">十二、长调、呼麦、马头琴与乐队《万马奔腾》                         齐·宝力高曲  赵东升编曲</span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                     长调演唱：阿木古楞</span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                    呼麦演唱、马头琴演奏：吉日嘎拉、呼和兴安</span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">十三、唢呐独奏《百鸟朝凤》                                                                           山东民间乐曲</span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                      唢呐演奏：陈力宝 </span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">十四、女声独唱《长鼓敲起来》                                                             李洁思词  金凤浩曲</span></p>
<p class="1"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                           演唱：谢琳</span></p>
<p class="1"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                            （国家一级演员、文化部优秀剧目展演优秀奖获奖者）</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">十五、合唱《北京市声》                                        根据老北京市声 亚雄改词  伯政编合唱</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                    《春节序曲》                                                                李焕之曲  孟卫东编合唱</span></p>
<p class="NormalWeb"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">       </span></p>
